<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .header { background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 10px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #777; margin-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; padding-top: 10px; }
        .invoice-details { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>New Invoice</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= customer.accountName %>,</p>
            <p>A new invoice has been generated for your account. Please find the details below:</p>
            
            <div class="invoice-details">
                <p><strong>Invoice Number:</strong> <%= invoice.invoiceNumber %></p>
                <p><strong>Billing Period:</strong> <%= new Date(parseInt(invoice.billingPeriodStart)).toLocaleDateString() %> - <%= new Date(parseInt(invoice.billingPeriodEnd)).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
                <p><strong>Invoice Date:</strong> <%= new Date(parseInt(invoice.invoiceDate)).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
                <p><strong>Due Date:</strong> <%= new Date(parseInt(invoice.dueDate)).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
                <p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> <%= invoice.totalAmount %> <%= invoice.currency || 'USD' %></p>
            </div>
            
            <p>Please review the invoice details shared in this email. If you need a copy in another format, contact the billing team.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for choosing our services!</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>CDR Billing System Team</strong></p>
            <% if (logoSrc) { %>
            <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="text-align: left;">
                        <img src="<%= logoSrc %>" alt="Cyvora" style="max-width: 120px; width: 120px; height: auto; display: block;" />
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> CDR Billing System. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
